--- .gitignore (原始)
```
# Maven build artifacts
target/
# Compiled classes
target/classes/
# Maven status
target/maven-status/
# Test reports
target/surefire-reports/
```

+++ .gitignore (修改后)
```
# Java/Maven
target/
*.class
*.jar
*.war
*.ear

# IDE
.idea/
*.iml
*.ipr
*.iws

# Logs
*.log

# Environment
.env
.env.local
*.env.*

# Coverage
coverage/
*.coverage
.htmlcov/

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.swp
*.swo

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Build system
.gradle/
build/
dist/

# Python (if any mixed)
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
```